The '''Outer Rim''' was a [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] quadrant in the [[Tatoo system/Legends|Tatoo system]]. Hostile ships were often seen in this area, so the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] restricted all travel to the quadrant.

